resolution: The bundled pm-kanban exemplar now registers kanbanProfile through the public ExtensionApi so installed projects can use pm profile list/show/apply kanban.
expected_result: An isolated project can install kanban and apply the kanban profile idempotently as an extension-contributed archetype.
actual_result: "Temp project /tmp/tmp.kDiR5fMIN8 installed kanban, surfaced kanban with extension source, applied it, and reported changed=false on the second dry-run."
